      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:1:57:15",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/57/1103",
      "text": [
        " «لاَ إِنَّ اَلْإِمَامَ ضَامِنٌ لِلْقِرَاءَةِ وَ لَيْسَ يَضْمَنُ اَلْإِمَامُ صَلاَةَ اَلَّذِينَ هُمْ مِنْ خَلْفِهِ إِنَّمَا يَضْمَنُ اَلْقِرَاءَةَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1103 - Al-Hussain ibn Kathir narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) that a man asked him about reciting (Qur'an) behind the Imam (during prayer).\nImam (as) said: \"No, the Imam is responsible for the recitation, but the Imam does not take responsibility for the prayers of those behind him; he is only responsible for the recitation.\""
        ]
      }
    },
